d":"67e519fb8299b3192c9af0a70255b2fae1b71dd7","tid":1965993,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"728f9b54dd27ae60a7ef0fc704038045bfac0bc9","tid":1965993,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b5f307811de6cb94e89c7bf10fd5af121632763","tid":1965993,"uid":37389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:22:23.000Z","msg":"仲未計依家市面上有一大批疑似係老鼠貨嘅日罩， 特別係fitty同奧田。批貨可能真係原廠出產 但係畀人偷咗出嚟係支那或者送嚟香港賣。 但係呢啲貨到底有冇做足曬所有消毒檢測程序就冇人知。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我見過一盒直接喺大陸運過嚟嘅奧田， 雖然望落正正常常，個filter嘅靜電亦都好強，但佢廠喺武漢，如果無消過毒或者係次貨，真係戴咗慘過無戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T02:41:26.000Z","msg":"奧田假左好耐喎清<br />\nBMC都係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:04:02.000Z","msg":"我有話唔耐咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4fa2b8eb90b9a71f49dbe47b44ff01bf3ae1ab9","tid":1965993,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:37:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f54e23f235b2380eb330e9908968ae24ddd22173","tid":1965993,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:01:52.000Z","msg":"測試口罩品質小貼士：<br />\n<br />\n1. 中層熔噴布會帶有靜電，不應出現小孔<br />\n<br />\n2. 撕開熔噴布時，應有韌度<br />\n<br />\n3. 熔噴布被撕開時，應看到幼絲纖維<br />\n<br />\n4. 以微弱激光照射熔噴布，應不會穿透光點<br />\n<br />\n5. 熔噴布應具防水功能<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：化學博士K. Kwong"},{"pid":"de6bc178bdae974bd06613fe2f5daf68bdf1df8d","tid":1965993,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"好多假日本口罩"}]}